{"ts": "2026-06-07T23:27:02.774772+00:00", "update": {"tools": {"messages": [{"type": "tool", "data": {"content": [{"type": "text", "text": "successfully downloaded text file (SHA: 14e35346190d0ff04ea56d634a34dbac593ed1c9)", "id": "lc_ebacbf99-67f2-40f5-8bfa-24e2f385f942"}, {"type": "text", "text": "{\n  \"name\": \"vue3-vite-starter-template\",\n  \"description\": \"Vue.js 3 Vite starter template with Pinia, Vue Router, Bootstrap and more.\",\n  \"version\": \"0.0.0-semantic-release\",\n  \"license\": \"MIT\",\n  \"repository\": \"https://github.com/kouts/vue3-vite-starter-template\",\n  \"packageManager\": \"pnpm@10.20.0\",\n  \"type\": \"module\",\n  \"scripts\": {\n    \"preinstall\": \"npx only-allow pnpm\",\n    \"dev\": \"vite\",\n    \"build\": \"vite build\",\n    \"preview\": \"vite preview\",\n    \"build-preview\": \"vite build && vite preview\",\n    \"lint\": \"eslint \\\"**/*.{vue,ts,js}\\\"\",\n    \"lint-fix\": \"eslint --fix \\\"**/*.{vue,ts,js}\\\"\",\n    \"test:unit\": \"vitest\",\n    \"test:unit-coverage\": \"vitest run --coverage\",\n    \"prepare\": \"husky\"\n  },\n  \"dependencies\": {\n    \"bootstrap\": \"^5.3.8\",\n    \"jsdom\": \"^27.1.0\",\n    \"pinia\": \"^3.0.3\",\n    \"vitest\": \"^4.0.6\",\n    \"vue\": \"^3.5.22\",\n    \"vue-router\": \"^4.6.3\"\n  },\n  \"devDependencies\": {\n    \"@commitlint/cli\": \"^20.1.0\",\n    \"@commitlint/config-conventional\": \"^20.0.0\",\n    \"@fullhuman/postcss-purgecss\": \"^7.0.2\",\n    \"@fullhuman/vue-cli-plugin-purgecss\": \"^7.0.2\",\n    \"@kouts/eslint-config\": \"^3.0.9\",\n    \"@vitejs/plugin-vue\": \"^6.0.1\",\n    \"@vue/compiler-sfc\": \"^3.5.22\",\n    \"@vue/test-utils\": \"^2.4.6\",\n    \"autoprefixer\": \"^10.4.21\",\n    \"eslint\": \"^9.39.0\",\n    \"husky\": \"^9.1.7\",\n    \"lint-staged\": \"^16.2.6\",\n    \"prettier\": \"^3.6.2\",\n    \"sass\": \"^1.93.3\",\n    \"vite\": \"^7.1.12\",\n    \"vite-plugin-html\": \"^3.2.2\"\n  }\n}", "id": "lc_43dd4815-bd5c-49dd-956d-8173f55548d0"}], "additional_kwargs": {}, "response_metadata": {}, "type": "tool", "name": "get_file_contents", "id": "adf6dbb8-2c5d-409d-b4fb-5cc7dc873e5d", "tool_call_id": "call_01_dWgoN2MT940VX81wcp017907", "artifact": null, "status": "success"}}]}}}
{"ts": "2026-06-07T23:27:02.775654+00:00", "update": {"tools": {"messages": [{"type": "tool", "data": {"content": [{"type": "text", "text": "successfully downloaded text file (SHA: 14cdb62b2e100f4ebf75f88cf5c58669437208e3)", "id": "lc_22dddd00-00bc-4b21-b3b1-5997171242ad"}, {"type": "text", "text": "# vue3-vite-starter-template\n\nA single page app [Vite](https://vitejs.dev) starter template, created to easily bootstrap Vue.js 3 apps.\n\n**Features**\n\n- Vitest for unit testing\n- Pinia for state management\n- Vue Router 4 for client-side routing\n- Bootstrap 5.3 for layout and styling\n- SCSS variables inside Vue components\n- Purgecss for eliminating unused CSS\n- Basic multiple layouts feature\n- ESLint config based on `eslint:recommended` with sensible defaults :relaxed:\n- [Prettier](https://prettier.io/) for code formatting\n- Automated release workflow with [semantic-release](https://github.com/semantic-release/semantic-release)\n\n## Project setup\n\n```\npnpm install\n```\n\n### Compiles and hot-reloads for development\n\n```\npnpm run dev\n```\n\n### Compiles and minifies for production\n\n```\npnpm run build\n```\n\n## Run your unit tests\n\n```\npnpm run test:unit\n```\n\n### Lints files\n\n```\npnpm run lint\n```\n\n### Lints and fixes files\n\n```\nnpm run lint-fix\n```\n\n### Customize configuration\n\nSee [Configuration Reference](https://vitejs.dev/guide/).\n", "id": "lc_7058de3c-83d1-43aa-9cec-8d9902f745b9"}], "additional_kwargs": {}, "response_metadata": {}, "type": "tool", "name": "get_file_contents", "id": "cb60bc7c-84a1-4b64-956a-cdbf4caac1f5", "tool_call_id": "call_00_3GUqWM57XjRGzwFGSu5p6394", "artifact": null, "status": "success"}}]}}}
